<view class="container">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">设置</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">调整推荐偏好，让“中午吃什么”更符合你的日常习惯。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">推荐方式</view>

    <view class="row-between switch-block">
      <view>
        <view class="switch-title">优先推荐喜欢和少吃的</view>
        <view class="switch-description">会更偏向收藏项、还没吃过或最近较少吃的选项。</view>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{settings.useWeightedPick}}" color="#a78bfa" data-field="useWeightedPick" bindchange="handleSwitch" />
    </view>

    <view class="row-between switch-block">
      <view>
        <view class="switch-title">首页推荐时排除今天刚吃过</view>
        <view class="switch-description">开启后，首页每次推荐都会自动跳过今天已经记录过的午餐。</view>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{settings.excludeRecentlyEaten}}" color="#a78bfa" data-field="excludeRecentlyEaten" bindchange="handleSwitch" />
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">数据选项</view>

    <view class="row-between switch-block">
      <view>
        <view class="switch-title">首次初始化时写入示例数据</view>
        <view class="switch-description">仅在午餐库为空时生效，适合第一次体验时快速看到推荐效果。</view>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{settings.showDemoData}}" color="#a78bfa" data-field="showDemoData" bindchange="handleSwitch" />
    </view>

    <view class="secondary-button destructive-button" bindtap="handleClearHistory">清空历史记录</view>
  </view>
</view>
